  "remarks": "Scientific and Production Association ‘Strela’, РJSC, is a specialised enterprise engaged in the development and manufacture of radar equipment for the surveillance and detection of ground and sea surface targets. The enterprise is engaged in development and manufacture of: battlefield surveillance radars, weapon-locating radars, artillery muzzle velocity radars, weapon control radars, air-borne equipment for air defence surface-to-air missiles, civilian radar security systems.",
